{"tid":457433,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬆郁朦甩圖文直播] 東北紅葉遊踪","createTime":"2017-11-04T00:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T01:06:40.000Z","uid":150902,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"73c91aab993ae6c707bfc37f8de95ef2bf8c25b1","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:51:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早兩年去過關西同關東睇紅葉，不過天氣同時間都唔多好，所以今年再出發 ....北上！！！ 東北走遍岩手宮城山形福島同東京近郊~ 不過小弟第一次開直播post,   希望儘量緊貼行程，同埋圖多數都係手機upload行先，影得唔好鬆郁朦勿屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/084828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F084828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a761901a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晨早機，原本諗住食返餐三哥先飛，點知太早未開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/084838_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F084838_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=065814f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後去咗東來居，32蚊盅頭飯加點心連茶錢加一，早飛嚟講算係經濟實惠~<br />\n<br />\n好，急要去廁所，陣間再講"},{"pid":"99271bf76c48ab415fe6d4558455447fd314aae8","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲圖點貼"},{"pid":"090b5acea4a39fe11279b5b14dc331a8b4e470c2","tid":457433,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"屌你 d圖係手機轉左90度先"},{"pid":"6f3a7ed614e9c31f0e5e838851873572a09b0998","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 d圖係手機轉左90度先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝巴打"},{"pid":"09c70d748dacc3bd8b0856cd89aa772db9cce967","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"瞓吓又醒吓嘅3個半鐘，終於飛到成田機場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/133927_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F133927_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b2c31ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個view幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/134828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F134828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fb8524bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一時間幾班機，多人到hihi"},{"pid":"55a4a871301c0c50106cde7c5017bd201d3d494b","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/142328_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F142328_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=474dc687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n步出見到稅關部份，感覺上成田機場有啲舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/142425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F142425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9a94428c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出到去又好光猛好新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/142530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F142530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8215ee3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買咗skyline加地鐵24小時券，2800鈤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/142857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F142857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d2b69731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n41分鐘就到上野，不過有些少貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b48f48afc3c1340e8b4b134acbe8e84eb336a74","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T23:02:35.000Z","msg":"尋晚因為無乜行程，又好眼瞓好攰，求其食啲嘢就瞓咗 .... 本身搭0742東北新幹線上盛岡 ... 屌，miss咗鬧鐘0712先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁極速洗面換衫出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屎忽撞棍我住嘅地方好近御徒町駅，用咗最快去上野嘅方法--JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係做咗樣好on9嘅事，明明今日會用JR pass,  但係我用咗張西瓜卡入閘 ... (又響上野新幹線個閘口唔可以用西瓜卡要用pass,  係咪要去返盛岡駅嘅人工口解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n響上野落車行過去新幹線月台都差唔多用咗5分鐘 ...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/065552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F065552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f1c15763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好彩最後都趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/065617_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F065617_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2f2b8bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭最快嘅隼號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/065625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F065625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1c4e27c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n似乎未上到札幌都係蝕住做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/070117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F070117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=003fbcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋晚落左好幾個鐘雨，今日放晴，希望陣間去到盛岡都係咁好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fe882a68d04e8da662eb053a964dc437be636f","tid":457433,"uid":114589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T23:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋晚因為無乜行程，又好眼瞓好攰，求其食啲嘢就瞓咗 .... 本身搭0742東北新幹線上盛岡 ... 屌，miss咗鬧鐘0712先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁極速洗面換衫出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屎忽撞棍我住嘅地方好近御徒町駅，用咗最快去上野嘅方法--JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係做咗樣好on9嘅事，明明今日會用JR pass,  但係我用咗張西瓜卡入閘 ... (又響上野新幹線個閘口唔可以用西瓜卡要用pass,  係咪要去返盛岡駅嘅人工口解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n響上野落車行過去新幹線月台都差唔多用咗5分鐘 ...<br />\n<br />\n好彩最後都趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭最快嘅隼號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n似乎未上到札幌都係蝕住做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋晚落左好幾個鐘雨，今日放晴，希望陣間去到盛岡都係咁好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝕唔蝕好難講喎！我那天搭10:20 gran class滿員咁滯。<br />\n<br />\n回程坐一般指定席哥卡車都係滿員就坐！<br />\n<br />\n我都想無人同我逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccabaace99b8e0a8bf758ca013d75b2bf60aabf","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T23:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>尋晚因為無乜行程，又好眼瞓好攰，求其食啲嘢就瞓咗 .... 本身搭0742東北新幹線上盛岡 ... 屌，miss咗鬧鐘0712先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁極速洗面換衫出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屎忽撞棍我住嘅地方好近御徒町駅，用咗最快去上野嘅方法--JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係做咗樣好on9嘅事，明明今日會用JR pass,  但係我用咗張西瓜卡入閘 ... (又響上野新幹線個閘口唔可以用西瓜卡要用pass,  係咪要去返盛岡駅嘅人工口解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n響上野落車行過去新幹線月台都差唔多用咗5分鐘 ...<br />\n<br />\n好彩最後都趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搭最快嘅隼號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n似乎未上到札幌都係蝕住做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋晚落左好幾個鐘雨，今日放晴，希望陣間去到盛岡都係咁好天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝕唔蝕好難講喎！我那天搭10:20 gran class滿員咁滯。<br />\n<br />\n回程坐一般指定席哥卡車都係滿員就坐！<br />\n<br />\n我都想無人同我逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同巴打一樣我都唔想迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能今日假期最後一日無咩人再北上，同埋聞說都係南下嘅客量係大啲"},{"pid":"9704eedc126da806e35cc9947e34eb9d32d53954","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"坐咗兩個鐘頭新幹線終於到盛岡，咁跟住搭都心循環線去盛岡城跡公園。盛岡城雖然係100名城，但因為時代嘅變遷，隨住江戶幕府、明治維新嘅改革而不斷拆卸，剩底到現代只係得返天守台同基礎嘅石垣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122138_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122138_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2a74be69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落咗巴士之後都係走陰天，行行下仲落雨 ...見到城外圍嘅紅葉都落咗6成，不過還好城上面仲有啲未落嘅樹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=03c16fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d3ed7479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=424e059e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陽光下呢棵銀杏顯得好燦爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122558_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122558_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9d3d7522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2cdf06b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行行吓見到兩隻主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係幼體，黑白色可能係大哥，對我戒心好重，而另一隻淨係掛住玩，好可愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=00507efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/122815_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F122815_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=72bab8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npost多兩張相機相，而家入緊平泉，陣間再講"},{"pid":"8be72d1db3157be4911471944f6fd1143a718080","tid":457433,"uid":48277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"巴打 我都岩岩去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上野 直剷上新青森 再玩落黎<br />\n其實東北新幹線好爆 屌 之前比人劃左坐中間 迫撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe6b93a623af6528d2804fc77b6410844b46aee","tid":457433,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 我都岩岩去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上野 直剷上新青森 再玩落黎<br />\n其實東北新幹線好爆 屌 之前比人劃左坐中間 迫撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特別早班隼號，成車高級社畜"},{"pid":"3f6f52f273439400f5cc553cb7980dfa84a2c396","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 我都岩岩去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上野 直剷上新青森 再玩落黎<br />\n其實東北新幹線好爆 屌 之前比人劃左坐中間 迫撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早班南下啲車我諗要再早啲預約，睇親搭個啲個個都係西裝大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我呢兩日想早搭個啲都搭唔到"},{"pid":"063e9395be48b78f7841314c1b620d4f227140b9","tid":457433,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 我都岩岩去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上野 直剷上新青森 再玩落黎<br />\n其實東北新幹線好爆 屌 之前比人劃左坐中間 迫撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早班南下啲車我諗要再早啲預約，睇親搭個啲個個都係西裝大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我呢兩日想早搭個啲都搭唔到</blockquote><br />\n好好奇係咁有人日日咁搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6244b0d55a76575960c5b21718d6f23c35b21fe0","tid":457433,"uid":145839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"樓主全程plan係點 用5日pass嗎？"},{"pid":"eacae42acd4dc360670dbe9092cc471e1f581501","tid":457433,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"仲以為禁錯post<br />\n東北紅葉post一入係譚仔三哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留明"},{"pid":"88d4cb59924751981d7862b02339a3c6ccf5769f","tid":457433,"uid":150902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主全程plan係點 用5日pass嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要買東北5day pass,  勁抵。<br />\n<br />\n我南下順路玩，第一站係盛岡，因為我去嘅日子再上青森都已經收晒皮。去咗盛岡城跡公園、中尊寺、毛越寺; 其實我去到嘅時候都已經尾聲，多數都係枯黃為主。接住再去仙台，本來想去鳴子峽，不過見到有巴打post話又係枯黃為主就去咗鹽竈神社同松島海岸。<br />\n<br />\n離開宮城縣就去咗山形，到山形山寺終於追到見頃，我有post過相上紅葉資訊post,  接落就去咗福島會津，留咗兩日，day1 就主力會津若松城同飯盛山，然後day2 就去咗只見線，夜晚就浸咗晚東山溫泉。<br />\n<br />\nbtw今日要出返東京喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0d0de0b62dd5758eb5e879a8afc2dc7d6f5376","tid":457433,"uid":51747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"巴打直播左一日就返東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b751ae05f466968c0a8980ddff9686958155466","tid":457433,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e64e90ee5423ef6f7deb2b4ca31aafd220e601","tid":457433,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"10月中先去東北<br />\n好掛住青森仙台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8158a6dc990f7333c1a49a4c8b2b4f00ddb1855d","tid":457433,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f951702ddd0bff2df00d59b8c5a16f68324d09b5","tid":457433,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:59:43.000Z","msg":"用左兩個禮拜時間都未出到東京"},{"pid":"56eb13a8b97ae40fd22349f064873302aee6ed30","tid":457433,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T22:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439d4b3d52237fc5f5441ce64499a2171bd8a92e","tid":457433,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d225fff12194b97af6fb46161d1a7057b7511be","tid":457433,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"仲未到東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}